<plot>John-John is young and black, growing up with his mother and stepfather in a boring suburb south of Stockholm. On one of the last days of the summer vacation, they rescue 10-year old Patricia from drowning at a public bath in Vinterviken. Her father shows his gratitude by taking them home to the wealthy neighbourhood where he and his family lives. John-John meets his daughter Elisabeth, and instantly falls in love with her. But it's a long way to go before he wins her love and her father's consent.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?641035</url></doc>
